                               NBER WORKING PAPER SERIES



                        RESTORING RATIONAL CHOICE:
              THE CHALLENGE OF CONSUMER FINANCIAL REGULATION

                                         John Y. Campbell

                                       Working Paper 22025
                               http://www.nber.org/papers/w22025


                      NATIONAL BUREAU OF ECONOMIC RESEARCH
                               1050 Massachusetts Avenue
